snippet.title: HIDE TIME CHAPTER 1 (Mascot Horror) | Full Game | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Welcome back to Hide Time! This is a remake of the original Hide Time, which I also played on the channel. We play as a brand new employee of Passion Oasis. We are trying to get the park up and running, but we get stopped in our tracks by a terrifying DJ Cat mascot! Can we make it out alive?!
 
KILLER COOL CAT MASCOT!!! (Mascot Horror) || Hide Time Chapter 1 | Full Game | No Commentary
